Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:40.64,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}憎恨至深 丑陋至甚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:43.98,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遮盖明月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:47.81,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}漆黑至暗 内心浑浊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:51.40,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只恨有你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:54.99,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飘忽不息 摇曳不止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:58.62,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如花朵般 传承信念
